1. 

Information regarding the following, as it relates to the undertaking 

concerned, and specifying the month to which the information relates: 

(a) 

the quantity of production and its net selling value; 

(b) 

the value of turnover, excluding VAT; 

(c) 

the number of persons engaged during a specified reference 
week; 

(d) 

total value of goods produced by the undertaking in the State; 

(e) 

total value of goods produced by the undertaking outside the 
State; 

(f) 

total value of merchanted goods sold by the undertaking; 

(g) 

total cost of merchanted goods sold by the undertaking.
